    <step order="6">UAT-C (no PCF binding): hard-refresh; switch dropdown to "All Records"; verify scope='all' is sent (no entityType filter), results span all record types in `spaarke-records-index`.</step>
    <step order="7">Smoke: Relevance Threshold + Search Mode are visible in side pane and functional (changing them re-triggers search per existing behavior).</step>
    <step order="8">Update `TASK-INDEX.md`: 109 đź”˛ â†’ âś….</step>
